parameters:
\F[nakosu_trouble]Nadeshiko: "The school doesn't even feel like a school
anymore... Where should I go to find the student council
room..."

\FF[ayaka_free]Ayaka: "Ah! Found you, Nadeshiko-chan~♪ I'm the first one
here♪"

\FF[ayaka_free]Ayaka: "Let's go wild together♪ Forget about being a hero of
justice, it's so boring... come on♪"

\FF[inu_free]Maple: "Exactly♪ Instead of pretending to be heroes of
justice, it feels better to get all lovey-dovey with
everyone♪ I want to fondle and fondle Shiratora-san's little
breasts and make them bigger♪"
\FF[inu_free]Maple: "Because... I just love breasts so much♪"

\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[inu_free]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Even you, teacher! We just parted ways a moment
ago..."

\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[syuu_free]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "Well, that's how it is. So, Nadeshiko, give up and
join us～♪"
\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[syuu_free]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "Akane-chan and... our master will be pleased too♪"

\F[nakosu_angry]Nadeshiko: "No, I refuse! I'll make my way through... and
reach it no matter what!!"
